data.description: This 3 bedroom house is situated close to town in Suncrest area.  Large fenced in yard for outdoor activities.  3 Bedroom 1 bath with full basement.  Two areas are partially finished below grade.  New HVAC and hot water heater.  Quiet neighborhood close to restaurants, schools, WVU campus and hospitals.  This is the perfect starter home both for location and price.
